{
  "stem": "1338.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, I got dysentery and I told Leib that I cannot make it anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to the hospital, and I went through the hell of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that was the block where Mengele was operating, where all the castrated and all the twins and everybody was there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were there as patients.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They gave us some drugs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at the same time, every week, they had a selection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were also very good at observing Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Germans were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Rosh Hashanah was the-- that was came-- that was about New Year's, September.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the eve of New Year's, they decided, have a big selection just to celebrate it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So Mengele came in and selected people and didn't select me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was on the other side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then, they left us, together, for three days, before the trucks came in at night with the-- and I spent most of the time talking to an engineer who worked in my plant, with whom I became very friendly in wartime.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His wife was in the-- with my mother in the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had no children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was older, and talked to me a lot for three days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I probably learned a lot about-- he was very highly educated, extremely intelligent man, multilingual and music and heart.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We talked for three days incessantly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He talked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I listened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At the end, there was a rumor that, at 9:00, they are coming with the trucks, and they will be taken away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he turned to me and said-- so the head of the particular place decided to keep the food until 9:00-- 10:00 so he doesn't have to give it to the guy-- these-- those who go to be, you know, gassed.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
